Description:
Pilot data for the impact of 'Integrated IAPT' services co-located in and integrated with physical health services, focused on people with anxiety/depression in the context of Long Term Conditions (LTCs) and/or Medically Unexplained Symptoms (MUS).

This pilot exercise is linked to the existing IAPT data set standard through the collection of LTC and/or MUS data from participating IAPT providers and services. More details at: https://www.england.nhs.uk/mentalhealth/adults/iapt/mus/sites/
Author: Nathan Abbotts
